================================================================================
ATTRIBUTION / CREDITS
================================================================================

wiki-base is an independent baseline (not a fork), built on publicly shared
ideas and prior art. The MIT License above applies to the original files in
this repository.

- The "LLM Wiki" idea — compile a persistent, compounding markdown knowledge
  base once and keep it current, instead of re-deriving knowledge per query —
  is due to Andrej Karpathy.
  https://gist.github.com/karpathy/442a6bf555914893e9891c11519de94f

- The skill set, directory schema, and citation grammar adopt structure from
  kfchou/wiki-skills (MIT, Copyright (c) 2026 kfchou).
  https://github.com/kfchou/wiki-skills

- The git-checkpoint codebase-sync pattern adapts ideas from Yiyi Sun / yysun
  (git-wiki, MIT, Copyright (c) 2025 Yiyi Sun).
  https://github.com/yysun/awesome-agent-world
